  -  ✓ Object Access (ALTA PRIORIDAD) - 4661, 4662, 4663, 4671, 4691
  -  ✓ Scheduled Tasks (MEDIA PRIORIDAD) - 4699-4702
  -  ✓ Policy Changes (MEDIA PRIORIDAD) - 4670, 4703, 4706, 4707, 4713, 4716-4718, 4739, 4864-4867
  -  ✓ Privilege Use (MEDIA PRIORIDAD) - 4674, 4985
  -  ✓ LSASS Events (MEDIA PRIORIDAD) - 3033, 3063
  -  ✓ System Integrity (ALTA PRIORIDAD) - 4618, 5038, 5056, 5061, 5281, 6410
